## ğŸ“ Coding Standards (Enforced)

- **C# 12**, **nullable reference types enabled**
- **Records** for data, **interfaces** for behavior
- **No static state** (inject dependencies)
- **YAML over JSON** (more readable for writers)
- **Directory.Build.props** enforces:
  ```xml
  <LangVersion>12</LangVersion>
  <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
  <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
  ```

